ir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sed1665702666179__table_d8729e1_d8730e1_d8731e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sed1665702666179__table_d8729e1_d8730e1_d8731e1__entry__2\">Menu item is displayed. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sed1665702666179__table_d8729e1_d8730e1_d8731e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sed1665702666179__table_d8729e1_d8730e1_d8731e1__entry__2\">\n Menu item is hidden and the menu accelerator for the item is disabled.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sed1665702666179__topic_d55772e1_d55773e1_d55774e1_d55775e1_d55776e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d512505e142\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sed1665702666179__d6620e20\">Use only in the preDisplay trigger of Menu objects.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sed1665702666179__topic_d55777e1_d55778e1_d55779e1_d55780e1_d55781e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d512505e151\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sed1665702666179__p_d84248e1_d84249e1_d84250e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hide</span> controls whether the current menu item is displayed.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sqy1665702665979.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$check</a><p>Return or set the checked status of a menu item.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/air1665702666109.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$disable</a><p>Disables a menu item in a menu object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ukk1665702596834.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>reset</a><p>Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to 0.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eww1719683180873.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>set</a><p>Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to 1 (TRUE).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ckm1665702665911.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger preDisplay</a><p>System trigger that is executed before a menu or menu item is displayed.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531935\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531935\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$hide Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $hide Return or set the display status of a menu item. $hide $hide = Expression set | reset $hide Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $hide Value Meaning 0 Menu item is displayed. 1 Menu item is hidden and the menu accelerator for the item is disabled. Use Use only in the preDisplay trigger of Menu objects. Description The function $hide controls whether the current menu item is displayed. Related Links $check Return or set the checked status of a menu item. $disable Disables a menu item in a menu object. reset Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to 0. set Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to 1 (TRUE). trigger preDisplay System trigger that is executed before a menu or menu item is displayed. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}